# RecordingMediaType

Recording file media type. 'Video' implies multiplexed audio and video. 'Audio' refers to audio only.

**Properties**

| Name  | Type | Required | Description |
| :---- | :--- | :------- | :---------- |
| VIDEO | str  | ✅       | "Video"     |
| AUDIO | str  | ✅       | "Audio"     |
